        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.acer.com/us-en/laptops/swift/swift-3-amd">Acer Swift 3</a>, laptop for personal use</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-in/surface/devices/surface-laptop-5">Surface Laptop 5</a>, laptop for work</li>
