        </ul>
        <h3>
          Next to my desk
        </h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.ikea.com/us/en/p/kvissle-wall-magazine-rack-white-90198030/">Ikea KVISSLE</a>, wall magazine rack</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/uppatvind-air-purifier-50498224/">Ikea UPPÅTVIND</a>, air purifier</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>
          In my pocket
        </h3>
