          <li><a href="https://us.kobobooks.com/products/kobo-nia">Kobo Nia</a>, basic ereader</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.jlab.com/products/go-air-pop-true-wireless-earbuds-black">JLab Buds Go Air Pop</a>, in-ear everyday headphones (wireless)</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.jlab.com/products/jbuds2-signature-earbuds-black">JLab JBuds2 Signature</a>, in-ear everyday headphones (wired)</li>
